@startuml
title Document Upload Flow Diagram

|Lecturer|
start
:Open course management page;
:Select target course;
:Choose PDF file;
:Submit upload request;

|Management System|
:Verify authentication and Lecturer role;
:Validate PDF file;
:Create document record with pending status;
:Push document into ingestion flow;
:Show "queued for processing" notification;

|System Handler|
:Run asynchronous chunking and embedding;
:Store chunks/vectors in RAG storage;
:Call internal webhook to update document status;

|Management System|
:Update document status\n(COMPLETED or FAILED);

|Lecturer|
:View document list by course;
if (Need to delete outdated document?) then (Yes)
  :Request document deletion;
  |System Handler|
  :Delete document metadata and related vectors;
  |Lecturer|
  :Review refreshed document list;
else (No)
endif

stop
@enduml
